file.name: apiDocs.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: "AWS Fullstack Website API"
  description: "Additional information resources for this API can be found below:\n-"
  version: "1.0"
  contact:
    email: contact@yourdomain.test
  license:
    name: "MIT"

servers:
  - url: "https://{domain}/{version}"
    description: "AWS Fullstack Website API server"
    variables:
      domain:
        default: yourdomain.test
      version:
        default: v1

paths:
  /api-docs:
    get:
      summary: "Retrieve the OpenAPI v3.0 specification."
      responses:
        200:
          description: "Return the api docs"
          content:
            application/x-yaml:
              examples:
                get-response:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/apiDocsResponse"
        500:
          description: "Default AWS error"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/defaultError"
      tags:
        - "Documentation"

  /info:
    get:
      summary: "Retrieve API version information."
      responses:
        200:
          description: "Get API version info."
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/infoResponse"
        500:
          description: "Default error"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/defaultError"
      tags:
        - "Documentation"

components:
  schemas:
    defaultError:
      type: object
      properties:
        error:
          type: string
      required:
        - error
    infoResponse:
      description: "Response for API version information request"
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        description:
          type: string
        version:
          type: string
  examples:
    apiDocsResponse:
      summary: "Response in case getting the api doc is successful"
      value: "openapi: 3.0.0 ..."
    emptyResponse:
      summary: "Response in case the querying the schema returns no data"
      value: "{}"

Error: notImplemented: path "/api-docs": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [application/x-yaml]
